.TH man 8 "14 Apr 2020" "0.1.3" "Orchid manpage"
.SH NAME
Orchid \- server script to automate common Debian deployments.
.SH SYNOPSIS
orcd [BREED] [BREED OPTIONS]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Orchid is an intuitive, module-based server script to automate common deployments on Debian. Targeted for System administrators primarily.
.SH BREED
This parameter should be one of the listed breeds in the help function, an empty or wrong argument will lead to the help function and terminate the program.
.SH BUGS
Bugs are tracked in the upstream repo at https://github.com/UpVent/orchid
.SH AUTHOR
Omar Jair Purata Funes, UpVent (omarpurataf@gmail.com, upventmx@gmail.com)
